{"snp1.7:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 1.7 ","snp1.7:0.2":"Vasalasutta ","snp1.7:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","snp1.7:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava savatthiyam viharati jetavane anathapindikassa arame. ","snp1.7:1.3":"Atha kho bhagava pubbanhasamayam nivasetva pattacivaramadaya savatthim pindaya pavisi. ","snp1.7:1.4":"Tena kho pana samayena aggikabharadvajassa brahmanassa nivesane aggi pajjalito hoti ahuti paggahita. ","snp1.7:1.5":"Atha kho bhagava savatthiyam sapadanam pindaya caramano yena aggikabharadvajassa brahmanassa nivesanam tenupasankami. ","snp1.7:2.1":"Addasa kho aggikabharadvajo brahmano bhagavantam duratova agacchantam. ","snp1.7:2.2":"Disvana bhagavantam etadavoca: ","snp1.7:2.3":"“tatreva, mundaka; ","snp1.7:2.4":"tatreva, samanaka; ","snp1.7:2.5":"tatreva, vasalaka, titthahi”ti. ","snp1.7:3.1":"Evam vutte, bhagava aggikabharadvajam brahmanam etadavoca: ","snp1.7:3.2":"“janasi pana tvam, brahmana, vasalam va vasalakarane va dhamme”ti? ","snp1.7:3.3":"“Na khvaham, bho gotama, janami vasalam va vasalakarane va dhamme; ","snp1.7:3.4":"sadhu me bhavam gotamo tatha dhammam desetu, yathaham janeyyam vasalam va vasalakarane va dhamme”ti. ","snp1.7:3.5":"“Tena hi, brahmana, sunahi, sadhukam manasi karohi; bhasissami”ti. ","snp1.7:3.6":"“Evam, bho”ti kho aggikabharadvajo brahmano bhagavato paccassosi. ","snp1.7:3.7":"Bhagava etadavoca: ","snp1.7:4.1":"“Kodhano upanahi ca, ","snp1.7:4.2":"papamakkhi ca yo naro; ","snp1.7:4.3":"Vipannaditthi mayavi, ","snp1.7:4.4":"tam janna vasalo iti. ","snp1.7:5.1":"Ekajam va dvijam vapi, ","snp1.7:5.2":"yodha panam vihimsati; ","snp1.7:5.3":"Yassa pane daya natthi, ","snp1.7:5.4":"tam janna vasalo iti. ","snp1.7:6.1":"Yo hanti parirundhati, ","snp1.7:6.2":"gamani nigamani ca; ","snp1.7:6.3":"Niggahako samannato, ","snp1.7:6.4":"tam janna vasalo iti. ","snp1.7:7.1":"Game va yadi va ranne, ","snp1.7:7.2":"yam paresam mamayitam; ","snp1.7:7.3":"Theyya adinnamadeti, ","snp1.7:7.4":"tam janna vasalo iti. ","snp1.7:8.1":"Yo have inamadaya, ","snp1.7:8.2":"cujjamano palayati; ","snp1.7:8.3":"Na hi te inamatthiti, ","snp1.7:8.4":"tam janna vasalo iti. ","snp1.7:9.1":"Yo ve kincikkhakamyata, ","snp1.7:9.2":"panthasmim vajantam janam; ","snp1.7:9.3":"Hantva kincikkhamadeti, ","snp1.7:9.4":"tam janna vasalo iti. ","snp1.7:10.1":"Attahetu parahetu, ","snp1.7:10.2":"dhanahetu ca yo naro; ","snp1.7:10.3":"Sakkhiputtho musa bruti, ","snp1.7:10.4":"tam janna vasalo iti. ","snp1.7:11.1":"Yo natinam sakhinam va, ","snp1.7:11.2":"daresu patidissati; ","snp1.7:11.3":"Sahasa sampiyena va, ","snp1.7:11.4":"tam janna vasalo iti. ","snp1.7:12.1":"Yo mataram pitaram va, ","snp1.7:12.2":"jinnakam gatayobbanam; ","snp1.7:12.3":"Pahu santo na bharati, ","snp1.7:12.4":"tam janna vasalo iti. ","snp1.7:13.1":"Yo mataram pitaram va, ","snp1.7:13.2":"Bhataram bhaginim sasum; ","snp1.7:13.3":"Hanti roseti vacaya, ","snp1.7:13.4":"Tam janna vasalo iti. ","snp1.7:14.1":"Yo attham pucchito santo, ","snp1.7:14.2":"Anatthamanusasati; ","snp1.7:14.3":"Paticchannena manteti, ","snp1.7:14.4":"Tam janna vasalo iti. ","snp1.7:15.1":"Yo katva papakam kammam, ","snp1.7:15.2":"Ma mam jannati icchati; ","snp1.7:15.3":"Yo paticchannakammanto, ","snp1.7:15.4":"Tam janna vasalo iti. ","snp1.7:16.1":"Yo ve parakulam gantva, ","snp1.7:16.2":"Bhutvana sucibhojanam; ","snp1.7:16.3":"Agatam nappatipujeti, ","snp1.7:16.4":"Tam janna vasalo iti. ","snp1.7:17.1":"Yo brahmanam samanam va, ","snp1.7:17.2":"Annam vapi vanibbakam; ","snp1.7:17.3":"Musavadena vanceti, ","snp1.7:17.4":"Tam janna vasalo iti. ","snp1.7:18.1":"Yo brahmanam samanam va, ","snp1.7:18.2":"Bhattakale upatthite; ","snp1.7:18.3":"Roseti vaca na ca deti, ","snp1.7:18.4":"Tam janna vasalo iti. ","snp1.7:19.1":"Asatam yodha pabruti, ","snp1.7:19.2":"Mohena paligunthito; ","snp1.7:19.3":"Kincikkham nijigisano, ","snp1.7:19.4":"Tam janna vasalo iti. ","snp1.7:20.1":"Yo cattanam samukkamse, ","snp1.7:20.2":"Pare ca mavajanati; ","snp1.7:20.3":"Nihino sena manena, ","snp1.7:20.4":"Tam janna vasalo iti. ","snp1.7:21.1":"Rosako kadariyo ca, ","snp1.7:21.2":"Papiccho macchari satho; ","snp1.7:21.3":"Ahiriko anottappi, ","snp1.7:21.4":"Tam janna vasalo iti. ","snp1.7:22.1":"Yo buddham paribhasati, ","snp1.7:22.2":"Atha va tassa savakam; ","snp1.7:22.3":"Paribbajam gahattham va, ","snp1.7:22.4":"Tam janna vasalo iti. ","snp1.7:23.1":"Yo ve anaraham santo, ","snp1.7:23.2":"Araham patijanati; ","snp1.7:23.3":"Coro sabrahmake loke, ","snp1.7:23.4":"Eso kho vasaladhamo; ","snp1.7:23.5":"Ete kho vasala vutta, ","snp1.7:23.6":"Maya yete pakasita. ","snp1.7:24.1":"Na jacca vasalo hoti, ","snp1.7:24.2":"Na jacca hoti brahmano; ","snp1.7:24.3":"Kammuna vasalo hoti, ","snp1.7:24.4":"Kammuna hoti brahmano. ","snp1.7:25.1":"Tadaminapi janatha, ","snp1.7:25.2":"Yathamedam nidassanam; ","snp1.7:25.3":"Candalaputto sopako, ","snp1.7:25.4":"Matango iti vissuto. ","snp1.7:26.1":"So yasam paramam patto, ","snp1.7:26.2":"Matango yam sudullabham; ","snp1.7:26.3":"Agacchum tassupatthanam, ","snp1.7:26.4":"Khattiya brahmana bahu. ","snp1.7:27.1":"Devayanam abhiruyha, ","snp1.7:27.2":"Virajam so mahapatham; ","snp1.7:27.3":"Kamaragam virajetva, ","snp1.7:27.4":"Brahmalokupago ahu; ","snp1.7:27.5":"Na nam jati nivaresi, ","snp1.7:27.6":"Brahmalokupapattiya. ","snp1.7:28.1":"Ajjhayakakule jata, ","snp1.7:28.2":"Brahmana mantabandhava; ","snp1.7:28.3":"Te ca papesu kammesu, ","snp1.7:28.4":"Abhinhamupadissare. ","snp1.7:29.1":"Dittheva dhamme garayha, ","snp1.7:29.2":"Samparaye ca duggati; ","snp1.7:29.3":"Na ne jati nivareti, ","snp1.7:29.4":"Duggatya garahaya va. ","snp1.7:30.1":"Na jacca vasalo hoti, ","snp1.7:30.2":"Na jacca hoti brahmano; ","snp1.7:30.3":"Kammuna vasalo hoti, ","snp1.7:30.4":"Kammuna hoti brahmano”ti. ","snp1.7:31.1":"Evam vutte, aggikabharadvajo brahmano bhagavantam etadavoca: ","snp1.7:31.2":"“abhikkantam, bho gotama …pe… ","snp1.7:31.3":"upasakam mam bhavam gotamo dharetu ajjatagge panupetam saranam gatan”ti. ","snp1.7:31.4":"Vasalasuttam sattamam. "}